We=E2=80=99re living in historic times. As Washington settles into the rhyt=
hms of a new administration, I could not be more thrilled to welcome Leigh =
Ann Caldwell to our remarkable and ever expanding partnership at Puck. Leig=
h Ann is an Emmy Award=E2=80=93winning veteran of NBC, CNN, CBS, and C-SPAN=
=E2=80=94and, most recently, a lead anchor and senior reporter at The Washi=
ngton Post. There=E2=80=99s nobody on Capitol Hill who is better sourced or=
 more plugged into the legislators, deal flow, egos, and inside chatter tha=
t truly drives the town=E2=80=99s agenda.

